biome.name: biome
biome.title: ecology biome
biome.description: A biome is a region in a world with distinct geographical features, flora, temperatures, humidities, and sky, water, fog, grass and foliage colors. Biomes separate every generated world into different environments, such as forests, deserts and taigas.
biome.descriptionClick: click to jump to the official wiki page
biome.usage: Click the category/tag above to display the corresponding collection, click the biome to display biome information
biome.biomeFilterPanelDescription: Select the corresponding filter condition, and the biome that matches the condition will be displayed after exiting the panel
biome.temperatureLineChartDescription: bar chart shows the temperature of different biomes
biome.rainfallLineChartDescription: bar chart shows the rainfall of different biomes
biome.categoryGenerateTreeChartDescription: tree chart shows the generate rate of different categories
